{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "main_14", "eventName": "慈悲燈塔", "entryType": "MAINLINE", "storyCode": "14-10", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "自光輝中奔湧", "storyInfo": "劍座與國劍合一，干擾戰場的源石風暴被暫時驅散，士氣大振的維多利亞聯軍開始反攻。Logos則在後方阻擊“靈幛”，並且獨自直面食腐者之王。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$newhope01_intro", "key": "$newhope01_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“傳說”，其意義是為人所賦予的。"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在我與路加薩爾古斯相識之前，你所握的“奇蹟”便已存在。"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "黃沙深處，本該死於天災的探險者們卻因這件寶物安然無恙。"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "寶物鑄成寶劍，我馱著那位年輕的沙阿攜劍步入漫漫黃沙。"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "38_g21_skystarry_r2", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我仍記得他在星空下，枕在我的鬃毛上休息時說的話——"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“它會擁有名字，但絕不會由我賜予。”"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然後，如傳說所言，他持劍斬殺了精怪之王。"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他沒有回來。舉世已無人配為這柄劍賦名，但傳說已然誕生。"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "英雄之劍。"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它輾轉於諸王之手，最終那位頭髮如驕陽般的獅子用它斬下了紅龍的頭顱。"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是你也熟悉的故事，維娜。"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "龍與獅最終並肩在它的鋒刃下立誓，共舉王冠。"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呵，英雄之劍不再殺戮，他們視它為“無上權柄”。"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_victoria", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它經歷了遺失，背叛，但其象徵權力的光輝再未黯淡。"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們如路加薩爾古斯所言，世代傳唱它被賦予的名字——諸王之息。"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無論重鑄多少次，工匠都能聽到劍身中的嘆息。"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們說，那是諸王的嘆息，嘆息榮耀不落的帝國已經沒有值得征服的敵人。他們如此期盼著。"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然“嘆息”的從來不是諸王，是這柄劍本身，是千餘年前被探險者自黃沙中掘出的“奇蹟”……但他們有權為這柄劍賦予意義。"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維娜，傳奇從不由英雄自己講述。"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你延續了它的故事。二十年後，或許孩童仍會傳唱……"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“維多利亞之劍亞歷山德莉娜，驅逐薩卡茲王的君王！”"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但這是你想聽的故事嗎？你又以何等身分握住這柄劍？"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "國王？英雄？或是人民？"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "50_g5_crackedhispdwarship", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_golden_ray", "layer": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#6$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（……老師。）", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#6$2"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_155_tiger_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維娜，接住你了！", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#7$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你做到了，維娜……", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#9$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_transmissionget", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "包圍“榮光”號的敵軍在公爵聯軍的進攻下開始撤退了！", "name": "戴菲恩"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維娜，撐住，我們馬上就能來與你們會合。", "name": "戴菲恩"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其他公爵的部隊都收到了開斯特公爵的訊息，接下來他們願意與我們典範軍共同行動。", "name": "戴菲恩"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至少，在打進倫蒂尼姆之前，這事算是說定了。", "name": "戴菲恩"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "通訊器中傳來一浪高過一浪的歡呼聲。"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "戰鬥在繼續。"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "諸王之息插入劍座，這不是結束，而只是一個開端。"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_396_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蒸汽騎士……在幫我們？", "name": "達格達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_396_1#7$1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#10$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，我想他只為諸王之息而來。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#10$2"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "推進之王的目光落在狼藉的戰場之中，那是蒸汽騎士戰鬥過的地方。"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她想要尋找另一道影子，可她一無所獲。"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "50_i36", "fadetime": 0.0, "xScale": 1.1, "yScale": 1.1, "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"image": "50_i36", "duration": 20.0, "xScaleFrom": 1.1, "yScaleFrom": 1.1, "xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "推進之王握緊了重錘，像每一次一樣，站在伙伴們身前。"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "繼續戰鬥吧。", "name": "推進之王"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "直至……勝利真的到來的那一刻。", "name": "推進之王"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "50_g13_warshipcommandroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "國劍啟動了。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從這裡抬頭看，那道金色的光，的確美到令人窒息。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "二十年前，我第一次在工坊裡見到我們的劍座雛形。從那時起，我就一直在等待這一刻。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "劈開天災的光芒，不再是神話，不再是流傳於街頭巷尾的英雄傳奇。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你能想像嗎？在此等光芒的蔭庇之下，我們的領民將不用再恐懼天災。我們的城市……將榮光永固。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個時候，根本不會有人料得到，它會被用在此時此刻。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "用在一場由“野蠻的魔族佬”掀起的戰爭裡，用在一片狼藉的倫蒂尼姆周圍。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且……是在那支典範軍的支持下，由我那位親愛的哥哥的遺孤親手做到。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "劍座事關我們在維多利亞數十年來的布置，本應成為開斯特的榮光，如今卻成了先王遺孤所創造的傳說的一部分。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "閣下，是我們令您失望了——", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "失望？", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_726_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……不。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#2$1"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_726_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“「榮光」號被拯救了，維多利亞被拯救了。”", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#2$1"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_726_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我又何必……失望？", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#2$1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“戰爭中的奇蹟”，我甚至能聽到我手下的親衛如此竊竊私語。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "想必你手下的“薩福克爵士”也有此看法，對吧？", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“詩人”的確應執行軍令帶國劍撤離，我會立刻確認——", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不急。瀆職還是盡忠，事後我自會判定。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然已成定局，國劍得失暫時不用考慮。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1"}, {"id": 130, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這未必完全是一件壞事。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "接通典範軍的內部通訊頻段。用聯軍的頻道。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "閣下，這有被監聽的風險。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_726_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "少言，做你該做的。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#5$1"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_transmissionget", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "CharacterCutin", "attributes": {"widgetID": "1", "name": "avg_155_tiger_1#5$1", "style": "cutin", "fadestyle": "horiz_expand_center", "fadetime": 0.5, "width": 200.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "欸，這是誰的通訊頻段？我沒打開啊——", "name": "因陀羅"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "典範軍的各位，你們做到了。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "*維多利亞粗口*？！", "name": "因陀羅"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "CharacterCutin", "attributes": {"widgetID": "1", "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_transmissionget", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "CharacterCutin", "attributes": {"widgetID": "1", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#1$2", "style": "cutin", "fadestyle": "horiz_expand_center", "fadetime": 0.5, "width": 200.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "公爵閣下……我還以為，至少你願意親自與我會面。", "name": "推進之王"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "的確，與您會晤的安排本已準備好。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但國劍啟動之後，戰場上的資訊都重新匯集到了我這裡。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1"}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "戰機稍縱即逝，我也實在分身乏術。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_726_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "推進之王女士，你們所做到的事的確堪稱奇蹟。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#8$1"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會重新評估典範軍在這場戰爭中能夠發揮的作用。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#8$1"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_726_1#8$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不記得我們的內部通訊頻段向你們開放了，閣下。", "name": "推進之王"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那現在，您可以看做它已經向維多利亞的所有聯軍部隊開放了。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_726_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聯軍的反攻會從奪回銀石崖開始——典範軍是否願意與我們一同創造奇蹟？", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#5$1"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_726_1#5$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……以公爵部隊的名義？", "name": "推進之王"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_726_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，典範軍不會，也不能隸屬於任何公爵的部隊，我向你保證。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#5$1"}, {"id": 172, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_726_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們必須是獨立行動的英雄部隊。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#5$1"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_726_1#5$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "推進之王"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_726_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "亞歷山德莉娜，你會知道的……知道典範軍對維多利亞來說，意味著什麼。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#5$1"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_726_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當下，我們確實站在同一邊。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#5$1"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_726_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "清點你的隊伍吧，我們得出發了。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#5$1"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "CharacterCutin", "attributes": {"widgetID": "1", "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "50_g1_originiumcanyon", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那金色光輝……", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#5$1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是諸王之息的作用。推進之王小姐和典範軍做到了！", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#5$1"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "戰場上的形勢將趨於穩定。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不再受極端源石環境影響，維多利亞的軍隊將很快展現出真正實力。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "軍事委員會在主戰場上的失利不可避免。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "即便公爵之間仍有紛爭，維多利亞軍隊的整體實力和持續作戰能力，都不是薩卡茲能夠比擬的。更何況，維多利亞如今士氣高漲。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "用不了多久，勝利的天平就會向維多利亞傾斜。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯……", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#1$1"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿米婭，當特雷西斯決定掀起這場戰爭，將無數薩卡茲的性命填在這他鄉的戰壕之中時，就一定已經料到了這一結果。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道的，凱爾希醫生。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#1$1"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可越是這樣，我就越忍不住在想……選擇犧牲當下的這麼多人，他們想要的，究竟是什麼樣的未來？", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無論那是什麼……", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "凱爾希抬頭望向紅色的天空。"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "風暴並未完全止歇。那些在倒垂的氣流中旋轉著的源石粉塵，只是暫時被諸王之息分開了，甚至正在變得更加激烈和瘋狂。"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或許他們所有人都一樣，僅為了延緩災難到來的腳步，就已精疲力竭。"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們距離深淵，只剩下一步之遙。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1072_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“返源”。", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1072_1#1$1"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$smallearthquake", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 3.0, "xstrength": 4.0, "ystrength": 4.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 30.0, "fadeout": "true"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "峽谷對面……有晶簇正在發光？Logos先生……", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#5$1"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1072_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再多的障眼法，也無法掩蓋鮮血的本質。", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1072_1#1$1"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1072_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我已將赦罪師設下的全部幻術剝離。", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1072_1#1$1"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "只要從那裡進去……", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line236"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 237, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "就可以找到真正的祭壇了。", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line238"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 239, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1072_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真相已觸手可及。", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1072_1#1$1"}, {"id": 241, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1072_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是……", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1072_1#1$1"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1072_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "陰翳也已迫近。", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1072_1#1$1"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很冷。太冷了。"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你又一次察覺到溫度的變化。不知不覺間，泥沼一樣的霧氣圍住了你們。"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……“靈幛”！", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#7$1"}, {"id": 253, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這麼多……", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#7$1"}, {"id": 255, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1331_1#1$1", "focus": "all", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1331_1#1$1", "focus": "all", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$frontline_intro", "key": "$frontline_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是食腐者在真正的祭壇之前設下的最後防線。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#5$1"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "孽茨雷要把我們留下。他不允許我們再前進了。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#5$1"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1072_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "死者的哀歌，正盤旋於戰場上空。食腐者的力量……近乎巔峰。", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1072_1#1$1"}, {"id": 268, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1072_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我已在天邊看到了死亡呼出的陰雲。", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1072_1#1$1"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1072_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "若是烈日不再，我當於此升起驅散濃霧的光明。", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1072_1#1$1"}, {"id": 272, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們……", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#7$1"}, {"id": 274, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1072_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "往對岸去。", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1072_1#1$1"}, {"id": 276, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1072_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "找到薩盧斯，摧毀“提卡茲之血”。", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1072_1#1$1"}, {"id": 278, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1072_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "讓戰場上空亡者的哀嚎，輕一些吧。", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1072_1#1$1"}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Logos抬手，指向對岸。"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "凝滯的霧氣重新分開了。"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1072_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——“擺渡”。", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1072_1#1$1"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_scrystalroad", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "極為簡短，極富力量。"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Logos既像是在描述正在做的事情，又彷彿只是施放了一段咒言。"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在你們面前，源石晶簇如波浪般湧動，層層疊疊地推進，終於抵達了峽谷對岸——形成了一座狹窄，但穩固的橋。"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1072_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "食腐者之王會追趕上來，需要有人拖住他的腳步。", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1072_1#1$1"}, {"id": 293, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1072_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我留在這裡。", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1072_1#1$1"}, {"id": 295, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Logos先生！你一個人——", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#7$1"}, {"id": 297, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1072_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿米婭，之前寄放在你那裡的包裹還在嗎？現在請還給我吧。", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1072_1#1$1"}, {"id": 299, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，可是你——", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#5$1"}, {"id": 301, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1072_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好，這樣就沒有問題了。", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1072_1#1$1"}, {"id": 307, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1072_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在，走。", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1072_1#1$1"}, {"id": 309, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "死亡在追趕你。"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你竭盡全力往前跑去，可能是阿米婭拉著你，也可能是Mon3tr拽著你，又或者是Logos用咒言推了你一把——"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你幾乎感覺不到雙腳與地面的接觸，卻彷彿感到有一萬隻枯骨似的手自霧氣中逼近，試圖抓住你的小腿。"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那些腐敗的氣息最終還是沒有追上你。無形的屏障籠罩著你的身體，將霧氣阻隔在咫尺之外。"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你知道那是Logos的咒言在生效。這一刻，報喪女妖的“詛咒”，顯得如此輕柔和溫暖。"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "50_g3_mainbattlefield_ex", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_rockbreakout", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_statuecollapse", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你順著崩塌聲看去。"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "橋消失了，就和它的出現一般迅速且乾脆。"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "濃霧又迫不及待地湧了上來。"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你想尋找那個熟悉的影子，或許因為距離太遠，或許因為霧太濃，你什麼都沒看見。"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "Logos會不會有危險？;我有些擔心……", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line330", "option2": "line330"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 331, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士，這是精英幹員Logos的決定。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1"}, {"id": 333, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他有權利根據當前的形勢做出獨立的戰術判斷。他認為由自己直面食腐者，我們繼續執行摧毀祭壇的任務，對局面是最有利的。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1"}, {"id": 335, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "告訴我，博士——你是否信任他，信任精英幹員Logos？", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1"}, {"id": 337, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "……", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line340"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 341, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "是的。;我相信他。", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line342", "option2": "line342"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 343, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼，你該相信，他一定會在我們需要的時刻，與我們會合。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1"}, {"id": 345, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "50_g1_originiumcanyon", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1331_1#1$1", "focus": "all", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1331_1#1$1", "focus": "all", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1072_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "腐敗的子嗣，我理解你們的渴求。", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1072_1#1$1"}, {"id": 358, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1072_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是死亡，不該如此喧囂。", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1072_1#1$1"}, {"id": 360, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1072_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "安靜。", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1072_1#1$1"}, {"id": 362, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_boneflute_low", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哨聲穿透濃霧，咒言如漣漪一般擴散。"}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無需開口，無需書寫……"}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "藏匿的死者無所遁形，“靈幛”的尖嘯化作長劍，自迷霧中穿透而出。"}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哨音嗚咽著言語，女妖之歌迴盪——"}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在薩卡茲古老的血脈中，在鋪滿源石的山谷中，也在無數戰死之人的哀歌中……"}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "燃燒的炮彈與巫術飛彈在戰場上空彼此交織。"}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一艘高速軍艦正撞向一座巫術堡壘。"}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "幾個維多利亞士兵正對一整支食腐者隊伍發起衝鋒。"}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "歌聲越來越響亮。"}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在那歌聲抵達最高潮處的一刻，一個又一個食腐者戰士，沉默著停止了攻擊，就如一面面靜止的旗幟。"}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們不再捕獵。"}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "死亡重歸大地。"}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "戰爭，回應你的歌聲而來。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "枯枝在同一時刻全部後撤，蜷曲，伏臥，回到死去已久的樣貌。"}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其中最為猙獰也最為古老的幾根，仍在不甘地糾纏角鬥，最終化成了一根法杖。"}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "杖尖落地，一個身影自濃霧深處顯現。"}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1339_1#1$1", "focus": "m", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哀琺尼爾……喪鐘王庭的主人。", "name": "孽茨雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1339_1#1$1"}, {"id": 396, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1339_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你選擇一個人留下見我。", "name": "孽茨雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1339_1#1$1"}, {"id": 398, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他的衣角浮動，吹散迷霧。"}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“靈幛”的白袍散落於枯枝堆積而成的森白山丘之上，長劍散落，如草如林。"}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "年輕的女妖側坐山丘之巔，沾染血跡的手指輕盈地撥弄著唇邊的骨哨……"}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "溫柔。悠揚。"}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement"}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4133_logos_1#1$1", "focus": "m", "duration": 2.0}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 409, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不……孽茨雷閣下。這裡沒有喪鐘王庭的主人。", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_4133_logos_1#1$1"}, {"id": 410, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "羅德島精英幹員Logos，特意正裝迎客。", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_4133_logos_1#1$1"}, {"id": 411, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我以死亡譜寫此曲，贈予閣下您。", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_4133_logos_1#1$1"}, {"id": 412, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 413, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 414, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 415, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 4.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 416, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 417, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 418, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 419, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}